                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1104" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0186</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10043 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农夫山泉的品牌塑造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">袁安府</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农夫山泉有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">市场营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农夫山泉；天然健康水；体育营销；高端水品牌</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">the NongFu spring; natural and healthy water; sports matketing; high-end water brand</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在上世纪九十年代饮用水市场竞争异常激烈的背景下，农夫山泉有限公司以天然健康水的品牌定位杀入市场，通过“农夫山泉有点甜”、“天然水与纯净水”的广告，掀起纯净水与矿泉水之争，并借助体育营销和公益营销等手段塑造起其天然健康水的品牌形象。但建立在千岛湖水源地基础上的品牌形象给农夫山泉带来了如下两方面的限制：运输成本的高企以及水源地出现问题的风险。为了应对水源地限制的问题，农夫山泉在全国先后寻找了四个替代水源，并针对新水源地带来的消费者品牌忠诚问题，开展了“天然弱碱性水”的公关活动重塑品牌形象；针对媒体曝出的水源污染的问题，开展了“寻源千岛湖”的大型公关活动。面对5100和昆仑山等新出现的高端饮用水品牌，农夫山泉如何维系其高端品牌形象，是农夫山泉面临的新的挑战。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the middle of the 1990s, the competition of the drinking water market in china is severe and brutal, whilst the NongFu spring Co., Ltd. came into the market relying on a natural and healthy market positioning. And then started the war between purified water and mineral water by the ads of “the NongFu spring water is a little sweet” and “purified water VS mineral water”, and initially shaped the natural and healthy water brand image by means of sports marketing and public marketing. However, the brand image which is based on the Thousand Islands Lake brought the NongFu spring Co. two limitations: the high transportation cost and the risk of problems caused by the water source. To reply the limitation of water source, the NongFu spring Co. successively found four alternative water sources, and promoted the “natural weak alkaline water” public relations activities to reshape its brand image, to solve the problem followed by the finding of new water sources such as the problem of customer loyalty. Specific to the pollution problem exposed by the media, the NongFu spring Co. carried out a large-scale public relation activity of “to find the water source in the Thousand Islands Lake”. Facing the emerging high-end water brands such as 5100 and the KunLun Mountains, how to maintain its high-end brand image will be the new challenge that the NongFu spring Co. to be faced.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司战略》、《市场营销》《公共关系管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略定位</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013-03</td>
